if bridge_candidates:

    if len\(bridge_candidates\) > 40:
        print\(f''''  ... and {len\(bridge_candidates\) - 40} more''''\)
else:

    print\(\)
    for i in range\(len\(beats\) - 3\):
        window = beats[i:i+4]

            if r == 1:

                    any_strong_suppressed = True
            elif r == 5:
                has_strong = True
                if b[''''madmom_score''''] < 0.5 * row5_mean:
                    any_strong_suppressed = True
        if cv < 0.5 and has_strong and any_strong_suppressed:
            bridge_candidates.append\({''''start_idx'''': i, ''''beats'''': window, ''''scores'''': scores, ''''mean'''': mn, ''''std'''': sd, ''''cv'''': cv}\)
    if bridge_candidates:
        print\(f''''Found {len\(bridge_candidates\)} relaxed bridge candidates:\\n''''\)
        print\(f""{''''StartIdx'''':>8} {''''BeatIDs'''':<20} {''''Time Range'''':<18} {''''Scores'''':<40} {''''Mean'''':>7} {''''Std'''':>7} {''''CV'''':>6}""\)
        print\(''''-'''' * 110\)
        for c in bridge_candidates[:40]:

            times = [b[''''time''''] for b in c[''''beats'''']]
            scores_str = '''', ''''.join\(f""{s:.4f}"" for s in c[''''scores'''']\)

    rbeats = row_beats[row_num]
    print\(f''''\\n{row_label}: median={row_med:.4f}, anomaly threshold={threshold_low:.4f}, normal threshold={threshold_normal:.4f}''''\)
    print\(f""{''''BeatID'''':>7} {''''Time'''':>8} {''''Score'''':>8} {''''PrevID'''':>7} {''''PrevScr'''':>8} {''''NextID'''':>7} {''''NextScr'''':>8} {''''Bridge?'''':>8}""\)
    print\(''''-'''' * 72\)

    print\(f''''  Beats > 0.5 score:  {above_half} \({100*above_half/cnt:.1f}%\)''''\)

    elif mn < md:
        print\(''''  --> Mean LOWER than median: left-skewed \(some very weak beats pull mean down\)''''\)
    else:
        print\(''''  --> Mean equals median: symmetric distribution''''\)
print\(\)

print\(''''-'''' * 80\)
for sec in range\(num_sections\):

    print\(f''''{sec+1:>8} {beat_range:<12} {tr:<16} {r1_sum:>10.4f} {r5_sum:>10.4f} {winner:>8} {margin:>8.4f}''''\)
print\(f''''\\nFinal vote count:''''\)
print\(f''''  Row 1 wins: {row1_wins}''''\)
